  "local_port": 58534,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are some alternatives to yelp in India?",
  "response": "If you're looking for alternatives to Yelp in India for discovering and reviewing businesses, restaurants, services, and more, here are some popular options:\n\n1. **Zomato**\n   - **Focus**: Primarily restaurants and food-related establishments.\n   - **Features**: Restaurant reviews, menus, photos, online ordering, and table reservations.\n   - **Website**: [zomato.com](https://www.zomato.com)\n\n2. **TripAdvisor**\n   - **Focus**: Travel-related businesses including hotels, restaurants, attractions, and experiences.\n   - **Features**: Extensive reviews, ratings, travel forums, and booking options.\n   - **Website**: [tripadvisor.in](https://www.tripadvisor.in)\n\n3. **Google Maps / Google My Business**\n   - **Focus**: General business listings across various categories.\n   - **Features**: User reviews and ratings, photos, business information, and directions.\n   - **Website**: [maps.google.com](https://maps.google.com)\n\n4. **Justdial**\n   - **Focus**: Local search for a wide range of services and businesses including restaurants, plumbers, electricians, and more.\n   - **Features**: Business listings, user reviews, contact details, and booking options.\n   - **Website**: [justdial.com](https://www.justdial.com)\n\n5. **Sulekha**\n   - **Focus**: Local services covering home services, education, events, and more.\n   - **Features**: Service listings, user reviews, and the ability to request quotes.\n   - **Website**: [sulekha.com](https://www.sulekha.com)\n\n6. **Dineout**\n   - **Focus**: Restaurant reservations and reviews.\n   - **Features**: Table booking, special offers, menu details, and user ratings.\n   - **Website**: [dineout.co.in](https://www.dineout.co.in)\n\n7. **Urban Company (formerly UrbanClap)**\n   - **Focus**: Local services such as beauty, cleaning, plumbing, and more.\n   - **Features**: Service bookings, user reviews, and verified professionals.\n   - **Website**: [urbancompany.com](https://www.urbancompany.com)\n\n8. **Facebook Pages and Reviews**\n   - **Focus**: Businesses across all categories.\n   - **Features**: User-generated reviews, ratings, and interactive engagement with businesses.\n   - **Website**: [facebook.com](https://www.facebook.com)\n\n9. **Nearbuy (now part of Groupon India)**\n   - **Focus**: Local deals and business listings including restaurants, spas, and events.\n   - **Features**: Discounted offers, user reviews, and booking options.\n   - **Website**: [nearbuy.com](https://www.nearbuy.com)\n\n10. **Swiggy and Other Food Delivery Apps**\n    - **Focus**: Primarily food delivery, but also includes restaurant reviews and ratings.\n    - **Features**: User reviews, ratings, and order histories.\n    - **Websites**:\n      - [swiggy.com](https://www.swiggy.com)\n      - [ubereats.com](https://www.ubereats.com) (Note: Uber Eats has scaled back in India, but similar services may be available)\n\n### Choosing the Right Platform\n\n- **For Restaurants and Food**: Zomato, Dineout, Swiggy.\n- **For General Business Reviews**: Google Maps, TripAdvisor, Justdial.\n- **For Local Services**: Urban Company, Sulekha, Justdial.\n- **For Travel-Related Insights**: TripAdvisor, Google Maps.\n\nEach platform has its unique strengths, so you might find that using a combination of these services provides the most comprehensive information based on your needs.",
